_aLatestUpdates._sText: I've procrastinated long enough, finally took the time to finish the tweaks i set out to do the month after the contest ended. I hope you enjoy this final version :)

_sText:
This is my map submitted for the Spring 2020 KSF Mapping Contest, based off the Swedish midsummer holiday!

It may not be midsummer anymore but here's the map in all it's glory:
  • 3 stages
  • tier 3
  • 4 bonus stages
  • Swedish references and easter eggs


Bonuses 1 and 2 were made by fellow swedish mappers Shena and Wakthor while I made bonus 3 and 4 myself. Most models were made by me from scratch but trees/flowers as well as most textures are from google.

When playing offline surf settings should apply automatically.
The bonuses are found in the little lake :)

If you're adding this map to your server I highly recommend you make sure the tonemap settings from the logic_auto are applied as well as use the dedicated trigger_multiple stage/bonus zones I made:
  • s1_startzone, ... , s3_startzone
  • s3_endzone
  • b1_startzone, b1_endzone
  • ...
  • b4_startzone, b4_endzone
